 628, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Your newsletter sign-up\", \"from\": 318, \"to\": 341}, {\"ngram\": \"the second day\", \"from\": 360, \"to\": 374}, {\"ngram\": \"track cycling competition\", \"from\": 378, \"to\": 403}, {\"ngram\": \"theParis Olympicsvelodrome\", \"from\": 407, \"to\": 433}, {\"ngram\": \"theCanadian women's team pursuit riders\", \"from\": 435, \"to\": 474}, {\"ngram\": \"the next roundand\", \"from\": 505, \"to\": 522}, {\"ngram\": \"contention\", \"from\": 533, \"to\": 543}, {\"ngram\": \"a bronze medal\", \"from\": 548, \"to\": 562}, {\"ngram\": \"the officials\", \"from\": 569, \"to\": 582}, {\"ngram\": \"the bell\", \"from\": 598, \"to\": 606}, {\"ngram\": \"their final lap\", \"from\": 610, \"to\": 625}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The trio, having been launched into their final kilometre by Erin Atwell, powered to what they thought was the line three-abreast but then the officials belatedly rang the bell, igniting panic in their ranks.\", \"from\": 630, \"to\": 838, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 691, \"end\": 695, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Erin_Hannon\", \"score\": 0.9999999997098712, \"rank\": 2.8905016042786867e-10, \"text\": \"Erin\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Erin_Hannon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Erin_Hannon\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The trio\", \"from\": 630, \"to\": 638}, {\"ngram\": \"their final kilometre\", \"from\": 666, \"to\": 687}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 737, \"to\": 745}, {\"ngram\": \"the officials\", \"from\": 769, \"to\": 782}, {\"ngram\": \"the bell\", \"from\": 798, \"to\": 806}, {\"ngram\": \"panic\", \"from\": 817, \"to\": 822}, {\"ngram\": \"their ranks\", \"from\": 826, \"to\": 837}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We saw one to go twice,\\\" Maggie Coles-Lyster toldCyclingnews.\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 902, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 866, \"end\": 885, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maggie_Coles-Lyster\", \"score\": 0.9999985358000946, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Maggie Coles-Lyster\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maggie_Coles-Lyster\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maggie_Coles-Lyster\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one\", \"from\": 848, \"to\": 851}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The first time, I was on the front, and we did not hear the bell, but I pulled up because I have been counting the laps as well.\", \"from\": 903, \"to\": 1032, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the front\", \"from\": 929, \"to\": 938}, {\"ngram\": \"the bell\", \"from\": 960, \"to\": 968}, {\"ngram\": \"the laps\", \"from\": 1015, \"to\": 1023}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was fairly confident that was the last one, and then they rang the bell as we were three across coming across the line.\", \"from\": 1034, \"to\": 1156, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the bell\", \"from\": 1100, \"to\": 1108}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 1147, \"to\": 1155}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We all had a moment of 'go - go go go!'\", \"from\": 1157, \"to\": 1196, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a moment\", \"from\": 1168, \"to\": 1176}]}, {\"sentence\": \"because that could be our race over.\", \"from\": 1197, \"to\": 1233, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our race\", \"from\": 1219, \"to\": 1227}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I think Ariane or Sarah took it away for the last lap, but there was a little bit of panic, and a 17-lap pursuit is not ideal - it hurts a little bit.\\\"\", \"from\": 1234, \"to\": 1388, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1245, \"end\": 1251, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariadne\", \"score\": 0.999998825401925, \"rank\": 1.1745917304295285e-06, \"text\": \"Ariane\", \"types\": [\"Q24229398\", \"Q178885\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariadne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariadne\"}, {\"begin\": 1255, \"end\": 1260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Jane_Smith\", \"score\": 0.9902614937494317, \"rank\": 0.009831392887446068, \"text\": \"Sarah\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Jane_Smith\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Jane_Smith\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the last lap\", \"from\": 1278, \"to\": 1290}, {\"ngram\": \"a little bit\", \"from\": 1306, \"to\": 1318}, {\"ngram\": \"panic\", \"from\": 1322, \"to\": 1327}, {\"ngram\": \"a 17-lap pursuit\", \"from\": 1333, \"to\": 1349}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sarah van Dam pulled out the last lap for the team, tellingCyclingnews, \\\"I think we were all a bit confused because we heard the bell.\", \"from\": 1390, \"to\": 1524, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1390, \"end\": 1395, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Jane_Smith\", \"score\": 0.9902614937494317, \"rank\": 0.009831392887446068, \"text\": \"Sarah\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Jane_Smith\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Jane_Smith\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the last lap\", \"from\": 1415, \"to\": 1427}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 1432, \"to\": 1440}, {\"ngram\": \"the bell\", \"from\": 1515, \"to\": 1523}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We saw different laps - and we execute this ride in training all the time, and when you see extra laps on the board, you are like, 'where are they coming from?'\", \"from\": 1525, \"to\": 1685, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"different laps\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1546}, {\"ngram\": \"this ride\", \"from\": 1564, \"to\": 1573}, {\"ngram\": \"extra laps\", \"from\": 1617, \"to\": 1627}, {\"ngram\": \"the board\", \"from\": 1631, \"to\": 1640}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But we came together, and we finished the ride well, that's all you can ask for.\\\"\", \"from\": 1686, \"to\": 1767, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ride\", \"from\": 1724, \"to\": 1732}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The team might have finished eighth out of ten, but they qualified to move onto the next round, where they will have to set the third or fourth-fastest time of the remaining eight teams to move onto the bronze medal round.\", \"from\": 1769, \"to\": 1991, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The team\", \"from\": 1769, \"to\": 1777}, {\"ngram\": \"the next round\", \"from\": 1849, \"to\": 1863}, {\"ngram\": \"the third or fourth-fastest time\", \"from\": 1893, \"to\": 1925}, {\"ngram\": \"the remaining eight teams\", \"from\": 1929, \"to\": 1954}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Only the top four teams, New Zealand, the USA, Great Britain and Italy will be eligible to compete for the gold medal.\", \"from\": 1993, \"to\": 2111, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2018, \"end\": 2029, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\", \"score\": 0.9434807510598311, \"rank\": 0.023717745629370266, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2035, \"end\": 2038, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999009929699948, \"rank\": 8.189412330757807e-05, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2040, \"end\": 2053, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.979447249198415, \"rank\": 0.01782189143931547, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2058, \"end\": 2063, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_