serious bacterial infection\", \"from\": 2442, \"to\": 2478}, {\"ngram\": \"contaminated food\", \"from\": 2504, \"to\": 2521}, {\"ngram\": \"the hotel\", \"from\": 2525, \"to\": 2534}, {\"ngram\": \"Atwell\", \"from\": 2536, \"to\": 2542}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think it was like a small victory to just even make it onto the start line today, and then to be able to put a ride together was pretty special.\", \"from\": 2549, \"to\": 2696, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a small victory\", \"from\": 2570, \"to\": 2585}, {\"ngram\": \"the start line\", \"from\": 2612, \"to\": 2626}, {\"ngram\": \"a ride\", \"from\": 2661, \"to\": 2667}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think it's pretty exciting for tomorrow - another day of recovery, and also getting the pre-race jitters out of the way will be key for tomorrow.\\\"\", \"from\": 2698, \"to\": 2847, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"tomorrow\", \"from\": 2732, \"to\": 2740}, {\"ngram\": \"- another day\", \"from\": 2741, \"to\": 2754}, {\"ngram\": \"recovery\", \"from\": 2758, \"to\": 2766}, {\"ngram\": \"the pre-race jitters\", \"from\": 2785, \"to\": 2805}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 2813, \"to\": 2820}, {\"ngram\": \"tomorrow\", \"from\": 2837, \"to\": 2845}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No matter what happens, Olympic newcomers Atwell, Coles-Lyster, Van Dam as well as Ariane Bonhomme, who was part of the fourth-placed team in Tokyo, can be proud of their ride.\", \"from\": 2849, \"to\": 3025, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2932, \"end\": 2947, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariane_Bonhomme\", \"score\": 0.9999990953219366, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ariane Bonhomme\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariane_Bonhomme\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariane_Bonhomme\"}, {\"begin\": 2991, \"end\": 2996, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9608689137594403, \"rank\": 0.035786940725659